        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center space-x-4">
          <a
            href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/marcial-fantini-8692b8290/"
            class="bg-transparent border border-yellow-500 text-yellow-500 hover:bg-yellow-500 hover:text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-full transition duration-300"
          >
